    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织表示米莱推迟阿根廷支出削减的举措是“务实的”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/imf-says-milei-move-to-delay-argentina-spending-cuts-pragmatic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱上周决定在其全面的改革法案中淡化支出削减，试图使其在国会获得通过，这是“务实的”，该机构对此举对经济产生的影响感到满意。该国 440 亿美元的贷款计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/imf-says-milei-move-to-delay-argentina-spending-cuts-pragmatic</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 20:00:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装继续瞄准红海，美国挫败也门附近的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/us-foils-attacks-off-yemen-as-houthis-keep-targeting-red-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，美国军队在几个小时内挫败了也门海岸的两起袭击事件，这让人们重新关注胡塞武装分子在美国和英国多次发动军事打击的情况下继续在重要贸易航道制造骚乱的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/us-foils-attacks-off-yemen-as-houthis-keep-targeting-red-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 19:52:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多伦多市长选择将财产税上调 9.5%，低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/toronto-mayor-opts-for-less-than-expected-9-5-property-tax-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大负担能力最差的城市之一的居民可能会在 2024 年面临 9.5% 的财产税上涨——但情况可能会更糟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/toronto-mayor-opts-for-less-than-expected-9-5-property-tax-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 19:27:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈佛 510 亿美元捐赠面临州税新威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/harvard-faces-new-threat-of-state-tax-on-51-billion-endowment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学今年将在其家乡马萨诸塞州准备两项法案，这些法案将针对该校 510 亿美元的巨额捐赠和录取传统申请人的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/harvard-faces-new-threat-of-state-tax-on-51-billion-endowment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 19:02:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德桑蒂斯承诺德克萨斯州从佛罗里达州派遣 1,000 名军队前往边境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/desantis-promises-texas-1-000-troops-from-florida-for-the-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯 (Ron DeSantis) 刚刚竞选总统失败，他表示，他已准备好该州国民警卫队的 1000 名士兵，协助德克萨斯州州长在美墨边境进行有争议的镇压行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/desantis-promises-texas-1-000-troops-from-florida-for-the-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 18:08:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登镇压以色列定居者对巴勒斯坦人的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/biden-cracks-down-on-israeli-settlers-who-attack-palestinians</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登周四签署了一项行政命令，允许美国对以色列定居者实施更多制裁——可能还有政府官员——参与针对巴勒斯坦人的暴力行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/biden-cracks-down-on-israeli-settlers-who-attack-palestinians</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国防部长奥斯汀就癌症和住院治疗的处理方式道歉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/austin-apologizes-for-handling-of-cancer-and-hospitalization</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀周四就他对前列腺癌手术和两周住院治疗的处理方式道歉，称他应该通知总统乔·拜登和美国公众。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/austin-apologizes-for-handling-of-cancer-and-hospitalization</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 15:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>唐纳德·特朗普因克里姆林宫档案而在伦敦起诉前军情六处间谍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/donald-trump-loses-london-case-against-ex-spy-over-kremlin-files</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 在伦敦针对一名前英国间谍提起的诉讼中败诉，此前法院驳回了他与臭名昭著的档案有关的指控，该档案涉嫌克里姆林宫与这位美国前总统成功入主白宫之间的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/donald-trump-loses-london-case-against-ex-spy-over-kremlin-files</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 10:08:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>天使投资者希望英国政府可能撤销一些新规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/new-angel-investor-rules-worsen-dire-business-landscape-for-women</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府承诺与企业家和投资者合作，以缓解因英国“天使投资者”计划更新而引起的担忧，批评者称这将使女性的投资环境恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/new-angel-investor-rules-worsen-dire-business-landscape-for-women</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 09:35:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着以色列与哈马斯战争的深入，加沙停火谈判取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/talks-seeking-hostage-deal-for-case-fire-in-gaza-advance-as-war-grinds-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，有关暂停以色列与哈马斯战争并释放哈马斯扣押的平民人质的协议的谈判正在取得进展，相关人士认为这项协议可能是结束长达四个月冲突的关键一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/talks-seeking-hostage-deal-for-case-fire-in-gaza-advance-as-war-grinds-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 23:21:29 GMT</pubDate>
